# assessment-scoring-flows

Core Assessment Systems:

## 1. Risk Assessment System
Importance Score: 85
Location: src/components/assessment/RiskAssessment.tsx

- 8-domain youth risk evaluation framework
- Risk level calculation using weighted domain scores:
  * 0-25%: Low Risk
  * 26-50%: Moderate Risk
  * 51-75%: High Risk
  * 76-100%: Very High Risk
- Auto-generates recommended placement levels (1-4)
- Domain-specific question weighting for risk profiling

## 2. Real Colors Personality Assessment
Importance Score: 75
Location: src/components/assessment/RealColorsAssessment.tsx

- Four-color personality model (Gold, Blue, Green, Orange)
- Trait mapping and scoring for each color profile
- Staff approach recommendations based on color compatibility
- Primary/secondary color determination with weighted scoring

## 3. Comprehensive Placement Assessment
Importance Score: 80
Location: src/components/assessment/ComprehensivePlacementAssessment.tsx

